Ways to get appPackage and appActivity:
--------------------------------------
adb shell dumpsys window | findstr mCurrentFocus     -  Both appPackage and appActivity

Ways to install apk into Emulator:
---------------------------------
🔹 Install APK using ADB
   adb install appname.apk

🔹 Unistall APK using ADB
   adb uninstall com.android.chrome

🔹 If app already installed and you want to reinstall:
   adb install -r appname.apk

🔹 If multiple devices connected:
   adb -s emulator-5554 install appname.apk

🔹 If multiple devices connected:
   adb -s emulator-5554 uninstall appname.apk

